-- Arathi Highlands
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The news of your victory satisfies me, <class>... a rare sensation. The Dark Lady herself has mused that our conquest of Lordaeron may be the only way the Forsaken can find true satisfaction, and pehaps even relief.\r\n\r\nBut it matters not. Our victory is inevitable. For your loyal service to the Forsaken, I award you in the name of Sylvanas.', `RequestItemsText`='You do this, an\' I\'m sure Malin\'ll be more than pleased with you.' WHERE  `entry`=26081;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Malin couldn\'t\'ve asked a worthier person to come here an\' aid us, $N. You\'ve done a grand job!\r\n\r\nHe\'ll be pleased to see what an overwhelming success our mission\'s been.' WHERE  `entry`=26038;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You place the rod in the keystone.  And a shudder is felt beneath you...', `RequestItemsText`='The Keystone is charged with tremendous geomantic energy.' WHERE  `entry`=26042;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Cleared out properly? Good. I doubt we\'ll even bother to lurk in Stromgarde. That ramshackle hole needs to be razed into dust.\r\n\r\nThe land would make a decent spot for a new Undercity in its place.' WHERE  `entry`=26027;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Excellent. The march of the Forsaken continues.' WHERE  `entry`=26053;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The signs of war are upon your garments, and sweat drips from your brow. Good, very good indeed.' WHERE  `entry`=26429;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='We survived the attack!\r\n\r\nWe could not have done it without you, $N.\r\n\r\nWe\'ll be heading out as soon as the tide rises. If you weren\'t such a promising hero I\'d offer you a place on my crew. But I can tell you have bigger fish to fry.\r\n\r\nEven if you are a puny $R....' WHERE  `entry`=26628;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Nice work out there, $N.\r\n\r\nThose scum deserved what they got. While nothin\' will ever bring me ship or me crew back, the death of those naga gives me some solace.' WHERE  `entry`=26055;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is but a prelude to the slaughter we will visit upon these lands. All will know our name.\r\n\r\nYou have done well, $N. Victory for Sylvanas!', `RequestItemsText`='I won\'t be swayed by empty claims. Have you proof of your loyalty?' WHERE  `entry`=26022;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I admit I\'m impressed, $C. It\'s a small comfort amidst all that\'s happened here.\r\n\r\nYou have fought the undead, struck back against the Horde, and honored the memory of the victims of Southshore. On behalf of the kingdom of Stromgarde, I present you with an official commendation, and this reward.' WHERE  `entry`=26117;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The goggles work perfectly now! Well done, $N.' WHERE  `entry`=26050;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='As Tor\'gan taught me, I transfer the power and the spirit of the raptors into this orb. It will imbue our warriors with the fiery strength and intelligence of the raptor.\r\n\r\nThe guile of the raptor is yours now as well, $C. Take it with pride, for the Horde!', `RequestItemsText`='My preparations are made, all I need are the raptor hearts.' WHERE  `entry`=26108;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Throm\'ka, $C. If your deeds for the undead are as great as you claim, I am honored to help you serve the Horde.' WHERE  `entry`=26084;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You friends with Goutgut! Him weird ogre. Smell funny.' WHERE  `entry`=26083;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I suppose I owe Thargas a favor for sending such a bold hero my way.\r\n\r\nOr perhaps he just wanted to keep all the clean-up for himself. Regardless, you\'ll find much to do here for the Alliance.' WHERE  `entry`=26139;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Apothecaries yet again. You think they\'d get the message. Let\'s see what it is this time...', `RequestItemsText`='We appreciate your help in looking for that courier, $N.\r\n\r\nWhile you were gone, Kin saw an apothecary come out of that same house to the south of here. I\'m confident that they\'re up to no good--I just need proof of it before we go off and do something rash.\r\n\r\nHave you had any luck yet?' WHERE  `entry`=26110;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You\'ve done a great service for us, $N. Thank you.\r\n\r\nI hope Kin wasn\'t too much of a handful down there. She\'s very friendly, but can be just as deadly when you\'re her enemy.' WHERE  `entry`=26116;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I know, $N. I should not have sent you.\r\n\r\nForgive me... the whispers of the past are sometimes too strong.' WHERE  `entry`=26911;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Say no more, $N. I followed up with an... "old friend" while you were gone. I should\'ve known better than to send you to those shards.\r\n\r\nWe\'ve both made a grave mistake in involving ourselves in this. Luckily, I "persuaded" my boy Gerrig to tell me what to do if this happened.' WHERE  `entry`=26346;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Very good, $N.  The last thing we need with the undead looming is a gang of common thieves distracting us.' WHERE  `entry`=26093;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The plague took our friends and family, but it was the Forsaken that took Phin. They\'re just as bad as the Scourge. I\'ll destroy every one of them with my own hands if I have to.\r\n\r\nWhen you\'re prepared, come let me know. We\'ll get started right away.' WHERE  `entry`=26114;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Refuge Pointe sent you? Good to know they\'re still there.\r\n\r\nWe\'ve got some interesting things to check into here, $C.' WHERE  `entry`=26113;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='The lethargy that overcame me even after the camps fell was so strong, I refused this gift when it was first given to me.\r\n\r\nNow, I am proud to do my part in the name of the Horde.', `RequestItemsText`='The fierceness in the eyes of the raptors will be matched by those of our warriors.' WHERE  `entry`=26107;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ahoy, $C. Any friend of Skuerto is a friend of mine.\r\n\r\nYou\'ll find plenty of work needs doin\' around here. We\'re not sittin\' in this cove twiddlin\' our thumbs by choice.' WHERE  `entry`=26336;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Valorcall was loyal to me in life. His death will not be something I bear lightly.\r\n\r\nBut bear it I must. I am Forsaken. My old existence means nothing.\r\n\r\nThe sigils are ours; Trol\'kalar awaits.', `RequestItemsText`='Have you the sigil?' WHERE  `entry`=26032;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='I hated the Syndicate in life as much as I do in death. To see the sigil again is a small comfort.\r\n\r\nBut we have much more work to do... for Sylvanas.', `RequestItemsText`='Only the Syndicate agents in Stromgarde will have the sigil. Spilling blood outside the fortress\'s walls will be a waste of your time.' WHERE  `entry`=26030;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thoradin was the founder of Arathor. Just as I join these fragments together, he joined the scattered tribes of humans into their first great nation.\r\n\r\nBut I\'m sure you\'re not interested in such drivel. Forgive me. Old memories are often hard to bury.', `RequestItemsText`='All five pieces are needed to restore the sigil...' WHERE  `entry`=26031;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='So the little gnomes proved their worth after all? I knew we kept those ankle biters around for a reason!', `RequestItemsText`='Ahoy, $C.  What brings you to the bridge?' WHERE  `entry`=26052;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<Myzrael speaks through the stone.>\r\n\r\nYou have done it!  You opened the Stones of Binding!  I can feel the shackles about me loosen, and freedom draws ever closer.\r\n\r\nYou are a noble $C, $N.  My rescuer!', `RequestItemsText`='This is the Stone of Inner Binding.  It is the strongest of the binding stones and must be unlocked for the others to open.' WHERE  `entry`=26041;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Thank you, $N.  We will inform the families of these fallen soldiers that they were killed in battle.\r\n\r\nIt will be grim news to bear, but it is better than the uncertainty of a missing loved one.', `RequestItemsText`='Have you retrieved any Stromgarde Badges, $N?  The Syndicate must learn they cannot profit from our dead.' WHERE  `entry`=26095;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Most superb, $N! The Captain will be very pleased! And just wait until word gets back to Fleetmaster Seahorn!', `RequestItemsText`='How did the goggles work? Did everything function properly? Adjustments can be made if necessary.\r\n\r\nOh, and I\'ll need those goggles back when you\'re done. I am sure Captain O\'Breen will have many uses for them later on.' WHERE  `entry`=26051;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Yes... I was once Prince of the fallen kingdom of Stromgarde. I was cut down by the one seeking Trol\'kalar.\r\n\r\nI rue my foolish life now. I serve...only Sylvanas.' WHERE  `entry`=26023;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This cluster of shards looks much like the Shards of Myzrael.  But the same feeling of security does not pulse through them.', `RequestItemsText`='Ah!  You activated these shards.  Already I feel more myself!\r\n\r\nBut alas, I am still far from free...' WHERE  `entry`=26039;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Ah!  You activated these shards.  Already I feel more myself!', `RequestItemsText`='This cluster of shards looks much like the Shards of Myzrael.  But the same feeling of security does not pulse through them.' WHERE  `entry`=26039;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='As the eldritch shackles are placed around the Shards, an unhuman wail is heard from far below.  The scream is followed by a roar.\r\n\r\nThe Shards of Myzrael no longer invoke feelings of warmth and security as they once did.  Now they pulse with an open menace... as if the thing beneath them holds ill will toward the surface.', `RequestItemsText`='The Shards of Myzrael are now strangely quiet.' WHERE  `entry`=26049;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='This is the fate of all who would stand in our way.', `RequestItemsText`='Speak quickly.' WHERE  `entry`=26029;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The shards pulse softly, and a whisper slowly echoes through your head.>\r\n\r\nHelp...' WHERE  `entry`=26909;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='<The shards pulse softly, and a whisper slowly echoes through your head.>\r\n\r\nHelp...' WHERE  `entry`=26341;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='My restless nights will turn to peaceful slumber when I have destroyed this orb. Thank you, $N. It is a chilling reminder of the terrible power the demons held over the orcs before Hellscream released them from their curse.', `RequestItemsText`='The burning in my blood... it grows by the day. The warlock must be stopped.' WHERE  `entry`=26025;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You stand before me as a figure of vengeance, and I bow down before you in thanks.\r\n\r\nWith that cow\'s death, and knowing that their seed will no longer spread over the face of Azeroth, I can put my energy into something more lucrative. I hope you looted their farmstead after you finished them off.', `RequestItemsText`='Kill them all and bring me their heads!' WHERE  `entry`=26428;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You amaze me, $N. Well done again.\r\n\r\nGive me a moment to cast the proper spell an\' you\'ll be ready.', `RequestItemsText`='$N, hello again. Have you found an azure agate yet?' WHERE  `entry`=26037;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Trol\'kalar, my father\'s blade... it seems like it\'s been an eternity since I saw it.', `RequestItemsText`='Have you Trol\'kalar?' WHERE  `entry`=26033;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Brilliant, $N. One item down an\' three more to go, based on my list. The other three items are all in Stromgarde.\r\n\r\nTake a rest an\' get your strength back--the next phase of my plan\'ll require a little more time an\' effort. Come back to me after you\'ve gotten a warm meal an\' some rest.', `RequestItemsText`='Our goal is the wand, $N. Focus on that for now.' WHERE  `entry`=26036;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='You took down Marez Cowl?  Well done, $N.  Well done indeed!\r\n\r\nMarez menaced our Stromgarde defenders, and it is rumored she was an emissary between the Syndicate and some other, darker power.  We are glad to see that she\'ll no longer ply her powers against us.', `RequestItemsText`='Greetings, $C.  You have a report to make?' WHERE  `entry`=26024;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Falconcrest and Otto?  Wonderful!\r\n\r\nHere is your reward, $N.  I am happy to pay it.', `RequestItemsText`='Hello.  Do you have a report to submit?' WHERE  `entry`=26079;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='At last, the Warchief\'s reinforcements have arrived. The Dark Lady has plans for you, as she does for us.' WHERE  `entry`=28572;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='At last, the Warchief\'s reinforcements have arrived. The Dark Lady has plans for you, as she does for us.' WHERE  `entry`=28619;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='Not bad. Since it\'s clear you\'ve got your head on straight, I was hoping you could help us with a more pressing job.', `RequestItemsText`='Have you had any luck so far?' WHERE  `entry`=26035;